text: Cichocki (feminine: Cichocka; plural: Cichoccy) is a Polish surname, it may refer to: * Angelika Cichocka (born 1988), Polish athlete * Chris Cichocki (born 1963), American ice hockey player * Jacek Cichocki (born 1971), Polish politician * Jan August Cichocki (1750-1795), Polish general * Lena Dąbkowska- Cichocka (born 1973), Polish politician ==See also== * Category:Polish- language surnames
title: Cichocki
